297
00:21:09,771 --> 00:21:10,771
Jo.

298
00:21:11,672 --> 00:21:13,471
Dobře. Jasně.

299
00:21:17,142 --> 00:21:18,142
Co je?

300
00:21:18,281 --> 00:21:19,612
