Kim Basinger.

322
00:22:03,721 --> 00:22:05,392
Kim Basinger.

323
00:22:05,392 --> 00:22:06,422
Je to Kim Basinger.

324
00:22:06,422 --> 00:22:08,062
Ale když jsem ji viděl,

325
00:22:08,062 --> 00:22:09,392
kašlat na Kim Basinger.

326
00:22:09,392 --> 00:22:11,461
