00:30:54,448 --> 00:30:55,648
Ty chytrolíne.

458
00:30:55,648 --> 00:30:56,717
Pojď sem!

459
00:30:56,717 --> 00:30:57,717
Omlouvám se!

460
00:30:58,317 --> 00:31:00,018
Co děláš?

461
00:31:00,088 --> 00:31:01,188
Omlouvám se.

462
